Mzansi's sweetheart Nomzamo Mbatha has deactivated her Twitter account. This comes after she had a live Q&A with her fans. One fan, who was watching her live, asked her how she dealt  with heartbreak. When Nomzamo laughed at the question, fans got annoyed, asking why she was laughing. Most tweeps dragged her because they were not impressed by how she responded. Others showed compassion, saying they could see she was clearly hurt. After the incident, she deactivated her account. Read: VETERAN ENTERTAINERS GET A HAND     